  "metadata": {
    "description": "Comprehensive mapping of all Taxi4U status codes for Voss Taxi",
    "version": "2.0",
    "lastUpdated": "2026-03-13",
    "notes": [
      "Status codes are SEQUENCES where each letter represents a status change",
      "The LAST character in a sequence represents the CURRENT status",
      "Example: 'BUGIMN' means the booking went through: B→U→G→I→M→N, current status is N",
      "vogn=0 indicates booking status codes, vogn=1 indicates car status codes",
      "Receipt can only be obtained for completed trips (l, N)",
      "M and I statuses should display which løyve (license/car) accepted the trip"
    ]
  }
